My babies made ME make it to Forbes 🙏🏻🥹

In my early twenties, I used to see some birthday cakes with Forbes & pics of people as a design on it.

A girl from small town, it isn’t a win for me but for all of us!!

It’s a WIN FOR ALL those who doubt themselves, not being from a big city, YOU CAN STILL DO IT & believe in your dreams…. 

My teenager me is screaming from inside that WE DID IT….

This has totally hit a girl from a small city Baroda (Vadodara) in Gujarat that dreams do come true.

Deep down, I have always been inclined towards entrepreneurship but this would have not been possible without your belief in me.

I thank EACH & EVERYONE of YOU from the bottom of my heart ❤️

Yalla Habibi 😍

What an experience at the WORLD’S LARGEST WATERPARK @aquaventureworld @atlantisthepalm which has broken the Guinness World record for the maximum number of waterslides in a waterpark.

Not only the kids, but even we had a BLAST.

It has 28 NEW ADDITIONS of slides with over 105 slides along with some great stuff to do.

You can choose passes depending on what you want to do and also have an option of JUST experiencing Aquaventure Park without staying at the Atlantis.

The prices start at 395 Dirhams for adults and 295 DHS for the kids. 
Also, the COMBO tickets include access to the aquarium!!

The timings are 10:00am to 6:30pm but on Saturday’s it’s OPEN until 10pm!!

The highlight is also the safety & a lifeguard at every point in few metres!

The lunch at @wavehousedubai had the most amazing menu with great options for the kids & also healthy choices for us!! And everything tasted YUM. 

It was a day well spent and I highly recommend this place.

SAVE this for your next trip to Dubai and SHARE it with someone who would love to go here specially with family ❤️

@tandemcommunication
